highlights.text: “Your Idol” by Saja Boys, Andrew Choi, Neckwav, Danny Chung, KEVIN WOO, samUIL Lee, and KPop Demon Hunters Cast is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Spain, up 39 spots at #137.
“El Fin del Mundo” by La La Love You and Axolotes Mexicanos has been on Top Songs Spain the longest, at 1353 days straight.
Quevedo has the most spots on Top Songs Spain. “YO y TÚ” is the highest at #3.
“What It Sounds Like” by HUNTR/X, EJAE, AUDREY NUNA, REI AMI, and KPop Demon Hunters Cast is the highest new entry on Top Songs Spain at #168.
